Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.00,0:00:18.20,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,就算看過所有的雜誌也是不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.50,0:00:22.10,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,只能在這裡搖頭歎息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.35,0:00:26.45,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒有什麼衣服適合我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.60,0:00:30.50,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,世紀末的流行色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.85,0:00:34.60,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,根本無法完全迎合你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.75,0:00:38.40,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你生氣 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.50,0:00:43.10,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,就像走在懸崖的盡頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.70,0:00:47.40,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,搖搖晃晃的有什麼不好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.50,0:00:51.40,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是這樣還是必須向前走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.70,0:00:56.00,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,對我來講 一點也不是問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.90,0:01:05.00,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是在最後時刻是不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.10,0:01:08.80,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託 別用那冷淡的眼神看著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.00,0:01:12.70,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我照著自己的意思去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.00,0:01:16.90,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,不然我很快就會崩潰的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.40,0:01:20.90,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,就像走在懸崖的盡頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.40,0:01:24.90,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,搖搖晃晃的有什麼不好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.35,0:01:29.40,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是這樣還是必須向前走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.70,0:01:34.10,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,對我來講 一點也不成問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.60,0:22:27.30,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,在這個看似有事即將發生的夜晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.80,0:22:31.90,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,最好做些祈禱 別閉上眼晴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.70,0:22:38.30,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,在月光如此澄澈的夜晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.85,0:22:44.60,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽曾這樣講 我們是因愛而出生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.10,0:22:55.90,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,接著一切都停滯不前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.50,0:23:02.20,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,看到了未來將要毀滅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.50,0:23:10.85,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 赤著腳 踩著大地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.05,0:23:16.30,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,越過彩虹 抓住天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.10,0:23:22.90,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish 緊緊握住胸前的十字架 早晨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.00,0:23:29.20,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,希望就會出現在你眼前 夜晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.30,0:23:35.40,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,用溫柔的光將你輕輕包圍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.50,0:23:42.20,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,Forever still for you. still for your love
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.50,0:00:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在瞬間之下 明白所有的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.40,0:00:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要開始 就不會停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.10,0:00:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天的舞臺是警視廳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.70,0:00:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,員警也是個普通人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.40,0:00:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對戀愛 事件 都很認真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.40,0:00:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看清唯一真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.00,0:00:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外表看似小孩 頭腦卻是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.00,0:00:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.50,0:01:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本廳的刑事戀愛物語（前篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.50,0:01:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是警視廳啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.70,0:01:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好大啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.50,0:01:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是處理過很多事件的地方吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.60,0:01:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這裡就像各警局的總部一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.10,0:02:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好興奮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.10,0:02:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.20,0:02:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們可是為了上次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.60,0:02:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個青色古堡事件的證人所以才被叫來這裡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.30,0:02:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是來遠足的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.10,0:02:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.10,0:02:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南還不是認為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.10,0:02:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以聽到一些未曾解開的事件而興奮的舞蹈著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.90,0:02:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對對 最期待的人就是柯南啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.20,0:02:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣子嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.90,0:02:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.10,0:02:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的你們就替我應付一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.10,0:02:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小哀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.00,0:02:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就是阿笠先生吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.90,0:02:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等你們好久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.00,0:02:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是搜查一課的高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.90,0:02:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請進 大家一起進來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.50,0:02:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.20,0:02:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 要你們特地來一趟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.70,0:02:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.80,0:02:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這地方還真漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.00,0:02:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.60,0:02:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的印象中應該是很髒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.20,0:02:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地上很多煙蒂的地方啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.60,0:02:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想大概只有外表而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.70,0:03:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對對 我想員警先生他們的房間一定是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.80,0:03:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.50,0:03:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好…好像沒什麼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.40,0:03:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.50,0:03:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有那麼意外嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.90,0:03:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為員警的房間應該都是到處都是煙霧彌漫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.00,0:03:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以為進來的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.20,0:03:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會有一些可怕的叔叔們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.90,0:03:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用斜眼看著這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.90,0:03:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是你們看太多員警故事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.70,0:03:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們看 我也是員警啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.10,0:03:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點魄力都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.00,0:03:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種樣子能夠抓到犯人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.20,0:03:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想一定不會有女朋友的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.30,0:03:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 目暮警部呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.30,0:03:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是他叫我們來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.20,0:03:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警部在那個銀行搶劫案的搜查總部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.80,0:03:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那個3天前杯戶銀行被搶走2億的那個事件嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.30,0:03:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.30,0:03:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候警部的太太綠夫人也在銀行裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.30,0:04:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被犯人給弄傷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.70,0:04:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以警部對這次的事情很認真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.40,0:04:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後高木刑事就代替目暮警部幫我們做筆錄嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.30,0:04:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.40,0:04:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我們現在去別的房間講吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.70,0:04:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為5點還有另外一個約會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.40,0:04:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你袖口的鈕扣快掉下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.00,0:04:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.10,0:04:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,領子也很髒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.30,0:04:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,襯衫也是皺皺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.30,0:04:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難不成員警先生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.20,0:04:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有女朋友嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.60,0:04:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.20,0:04:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我介紹我妹妹的孫女給你認識吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.50,0:04:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.90,0:04:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也有喜歡的人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.70,0:04:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.70,0:04:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些小孩是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.70,0:04:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迷路的小孩應該送到生活安全部門吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.10,0:04:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.40,0:04:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些小孩是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.50,0:04:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這姐姐是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.00,0:04:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.30,0:04:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼臉紅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.10,0:05:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.10,0:05:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是高木刑事的愛人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.80,0:05:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把自己的愛人帶到這種地方行嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.60,0:05:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.40,0:05:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫做佐藤美和子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.30,0:05:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是個女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.70,0:05:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我也是搜查一課 強行犯三系的女員警哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.70,0:05:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女員警
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.90,0:05:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好威風啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.00,0:05:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些小孩到底是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.70,0:05:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們是那個青色古堡事件的證人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.10,0:05:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難不成就是當時立功的那些小孩子嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.40,0:05:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.50,0:05:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為那場火災的事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.10,0:05:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們請他們回來做筆錄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.80,0:05:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我想起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.00,0:05:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐是在競技場事件的時候裡面的那個女員警吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.10,0:05:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那個時候超威風的姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.20,0:05:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.20,0:05:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們就是當時在那裡跑來跑去的小孩子們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.20,0:05:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒有跑來跑去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.40,0:06:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也有在幫忙做調查的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.90,0:06:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也沒有妨礙你們啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.40,0:06:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.90,0:06:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們偵探團是為了正義而做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.90,0:06:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.00,0:06:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.40,0:06:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.60,0:06:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,競技場的事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.30,0:06:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有青色古堡的事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.10,0:06:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許都是多虧你們才能破案的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.00,0:06:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.40,0:06:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你記住這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.20,0:06:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[正義]這兩個字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.50,0:06:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是可以隨便拿出來玩的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.70,0:06:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是應該靜靜的收藏在自己心中才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.80,0:06:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.00,0:06:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位小偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.40,0:06:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.30,0:06:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會不會太嚴厲了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.00,0:06:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.80,0:06:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是為什麼呢 佐藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.30,0:06:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不是和目暮警部一起去調查2億搶劫事件了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.10,0:06:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是為了這個事回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.50,0:06:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我昨晚接到被搶劫的那個銀行行長打來的電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.70,0:06:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說想起一些事情想要跟我們講
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.90,0:07:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後來約定在這裡見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.60,0:07:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夫妻二人2點在這裡碰面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.60,0:07:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼夫妻二人都要來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.00,0:07:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為案發當時行長的妻子也在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.00,0:07:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她被犯人用槍抵住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.50,0:07:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想該不會是因為想起當時的事情吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.30,0:07:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過很奇怪耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.20,0:07:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚我也接到行長太太的電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.50,0:07:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想告訴我們有關犯人的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.20,0:07:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,5點她自己會一個人來警察局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.70,0:07:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這件事分行行長也講過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.20,0:07:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他怕妻子會被犯人攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.80,0:07:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以想趁白天二人一起過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.10,0:07:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.80,0:07:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 交通課的由美今天有沒有亂講些什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.30,0:07:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得我昨晚喝醉以後告訴了她一些無聊的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.20,0:07:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我卻一點都不記得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.20,0:07:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不 沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.30,0:07:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說 高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.10,0:08:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚美和子喝醉了然後我問了她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.20,0:08:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她真的有喜歡的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.40,0:08:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在搜查一課裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.60,0:08:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定就是那個 說不定哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.80,0:08:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是羡慕死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.80,0:08:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤刑事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.00,0:08:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把東都銀行的分行行長帶來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.10,0:08:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了 請過來這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.20,0:08:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總算趕上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.20,0:08:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 夫人沒和你一起來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.80,0:08:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為銀行那邊有點事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.20,0:08:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以就和我太太約在這裡見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.60,0:08:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她還沒來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.40,0:08:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.40,0:08:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了 她還在睡覺嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.20,0:08:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,員警先生 可以借個電話嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.30,0:08:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.70,0:08:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第三次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.50,0:09:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼三次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.70,0:09:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他看手錶的次數
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.80,0:09:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是增尾家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.10,0:09:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.10,0:09:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在在警局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.50,0:09:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我找人來聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.00,0:09:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.60,0:09:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是昨晚那個員警嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.80,0:09:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好像記得你叫高木先生吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.50,0:09:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.70,0:09:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夫人好像還在家裡 到底怎麼了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.80,0:09:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 怎麼 約定的時間不是5點嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.90,0:09:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 你先生說兩點鐘的時候兩個人會一起過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.70,0:09:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道有這一回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.50,0:09:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.60,0:09:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你說什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.40,0:09:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.40,0:09:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 夫人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.10,0:09:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請回答 夫人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.30,0:10:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了 夫人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.30,0:10:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高木 叫機搜隊準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.90,0:10:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去開車過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.60,0:10:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.70,0:10:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼是機搜隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.30,0:10:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是調查事件時會出動機動搜查隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.40,0:10:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.90,0:10:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.40,0:10:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.60,0:10:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太太 我太太不會有事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.10,0:10:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這兩三天內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.30,0:10:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們有沒有感覺到什麼可疑的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.40,0:10:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可疑的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.90,0:10:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 對了 我太太說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.30,0:10:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到外面有個可疑的人在外面徘徊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.80,0:10:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想大概是其中一個犯人認為被夫人看到了樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.40,0:10:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以想過來殺人滅口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.20,0:10:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.90,0:10:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是 不 也許只是個普通盜竊案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.90,0:10:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電話是連接到警局的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.40,0:10:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別認為這是個普通的小偷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.00,0:10:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南…你什麼時候上車的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.70,0:11:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.70,0:11:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間讓他下車了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.20,0:11:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在最重要的就是去找夫人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.50,0:11:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孩子 別咬到舌頭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.00,0:11:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 加代 加代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.50,0:11:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請員警先生到二樓去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.00,0:11:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去大廳看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.10,0:11:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.30,0:11:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.60,0:11:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.30,0:11:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,窗戶開了個洞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.60,0:11:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是從外部闖進來的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.00,0:11:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.80,0:11:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加代 加代她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.70,0:12:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夫人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.90,0:12:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我去叫救護車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.50,0:12:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 要叫的應該是機搜和鑑識課
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.60,0:12:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她已經斷氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.10,0:12:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.80,0:12:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫我記一下時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.30,0:12:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,14點46分 發現屍體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.40,0:12:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是誰 到底是誰這麼殘忍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.00,0:12:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道真的是那些強盜嗎 員警先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.60,0:12:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.10,0:12:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要進入這個房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.60,0:12:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算不注意也會看到夫人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.50,0:12:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是這個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.90,0:12:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我發現玻璃有洞走到窗戶那邊去的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.60,0:12:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個字都沒有講
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.30,0:12:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是為什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.70,0:12:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通常會有人去攻擊正在講電話的人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.20,0:12:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不小心就有可能會被別人聽見自己的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.20,0:13:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通常聽電話的人會因為懷疑而跑過來看的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.00,0:13:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且還有他在警視廳講的那些話和一些舉動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.10,0:13:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難不成 設計這個殺人計畫的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.60,0:13:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫非
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.50,0:13:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被殺害的是增尾加代女士 42歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.00,0:13:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兇器就是被插入加代太太背部的那把刀子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.40,0:13:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有掙扎過的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.50,0:13:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想是一刀斃命吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.80,0:13:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想殺害的時間大概就是被害者發出慘叫的時候吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.40,0:13:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤刑事 你聽到了被害者的慘叫聲嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.90,0:13:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被害者的丈夫正好從警視廳打電話到這裡來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.70,0:13:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我不小心把電話的擴音器打開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.70,0:13:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.20,0:13:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在電話裡聽到我太太慘叫的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.90,0:14:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼被害者是在講電話時被某人從背後攻擊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.70,0:14:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我認為她不是只有在聽電話而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.00,0:14:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想這個人應該是一邊騎車一邊聽電話的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.20,0:14:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且你們看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.30,0:14:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個人身上有汗 衣服也是濕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.00,0:14:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人類死亡之後新陳代謝就會停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.80,0:14:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算溫度上升也不會流汗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.30,0:14:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她流的汗現在還沒有幹掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.70,0:14:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說這個人在被殺害之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.90,0:14:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正在做會流汗的什麼事情吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.60,0:14:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我看過鞋櫃 裡面沒有慢跑用的球鞋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.50,0:14:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這間房子裡面唯一可以讓她流汗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.70,0:14:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是在遺體附近的這輛電動車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.40,0:14:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼可以隨意跑進來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.40,0:14:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.40,0:14:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孩子 我還不知道你叫什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.50,0:15:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,江戶川柯南 是個偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.10,0:15:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偵…偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.50,0:15:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就是住在毛利偵探家的小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.20,0:15:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.40,0:15:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才會知道這些事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.80,0:15:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼男孩 長大後去當員警吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.50,0:15:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果派到我們這單位來的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.20,0:15:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們會好好照顧你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.40,0:15:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.90,0:15:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.00,0:15:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼佐藤刑事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.40,0:15:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們出去問問鄰居 看有沒有目擊者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.70,0:15:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有這個家也要仔細的調查才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.60,0:15:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有可能是為了偷錢而殺人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.60,0:15:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.60,0:15:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 這並不是普通的盜竊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.30,0:15:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯人的目標從一開始就是這位夫人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.10,0:15:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是這麼認為的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.50,0:15:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白…白鳥警部補
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.00,0:15:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不是警部補了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.20,0:15:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我已經升級為警部了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.90,0:16:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以這次的事件由我來負責
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.60,0:16:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不錯 專門奉承的角色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.20,0:16:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,升級總是特別快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.90,0:16:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不嫌棄的話 讓我加入你的未婚妻候補名單吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.30,0:16:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 我很樂意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.90,0:16:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難…難道佐藤小姐喜歡的人是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.20,0:16:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白鳥先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.40,0:16:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.10,0:16:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,值勤中怎麼可以胡思亂想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.60,0:16:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你為什麼認為不是盜竊呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.50,0:16:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是你們在電話中聽到被害者的叫聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.50,0:16:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通常盜竊犯是不會攻擊正在講電話的人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.80,0:16:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果被發現而大叫的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.30,0:16:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盜竊犯早就會逃掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.60,0:16:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且被害者今天好像是為了什麼事要到警察局去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.60,0:16:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 她說那個銀行搶劫事件想起一些事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.60,0:16:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以準備和丈夫一起過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.80,0:17:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是到了約定的時間還沒出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.60,0:17:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她丈夫有點擔心所以才打電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.70,0:17:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼她有沒有說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.70,0:17:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這電話是從警察局打來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.20,0:17:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.70,0:17:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當我接電話的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.20,0:17:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她說[你是昨天那個員警先生吧]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.30,0:17:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就不會錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.60,0:17:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯人為了不想讓被害者繼續和員警講話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.90,0:17:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會在被害者通話的時候把她殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.10,0:17:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 這樣一來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.50,0:17:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 我想那個犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.80,0:17:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是那個二人組的搶劫犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.90,0:17:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被害者在那次的事件中被犯人用槍抵著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.10,0:17:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以和其中一個搶劫犯非常的接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.50,0:17:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想犯人以為自己被識破了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.70,0:17:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以殺人滅口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.60,0:17:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且被害者作為人質時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.40,0:17:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像還拼命掙扎 曾抓過犯人的面罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.10,0:17:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.00,0:17:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為太難對付了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.10,0:18:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以換了碰巧去銀行的目暮夫人做第二個人質
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.50,0:18:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然目暮夫人是主動提出要做人質的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.50,0:18:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我太太昨晚說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.20,0:18:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼外國人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.00,0:18:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 就是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.90,0:18:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想夫人就是想要告訴我們那個犯人的特徵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.90,0:18:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高木 聯絡特搜總部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.50,0:18:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其中一個犯人應該是個外國人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.10,0:18:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.30,0:18:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你們不覺得奇怪嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.00,0:18:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看 電動車的後面只有兩公尺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.40,0:18:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後面沒有門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.50,0:18:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼犯人會從後面攻擊正在騎電動車的夫人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.70,0:18:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是這個孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.50,0:18:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你認識他嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.30,0:18:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直跟在毛利先生旁邊的那個小偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.90,0:18:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到你這麼出名 孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.50,0:18:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.60,0:19:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼 高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.60,0:19:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.10,0:19:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,員警先生也覺得很奇怪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.00,0:19:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.70,0:19:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算她是從後面被刺死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.10,0:19:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不一定是從後面被偷襲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.00,0:19:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有可能是被害者看到犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.90,0:19:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正想要逃走 而被刺死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.70,0:19:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是這樣的話 遺體應該
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.10,0:19:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒在距離電動車更遠一點的地方啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.90,0:19:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電話也掉在附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.00,0:19:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是倒在別的地方的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.00,0:19:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該有汗水的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.70,0:19:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.80,0:19:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有理由故意要把被害人搬到電動車旁邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.20,0:19:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣說也對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.40,0:19:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,增尾先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.20,0:19:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你太太她一直都有騎電動車的習慣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.20,0:19:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.20,0:19:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她每天下午2點的時候都會在這裡騎電單車做運動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.30,0:19:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 你們早上都幾點起床
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.20,0:20:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我要到銀行上班一早就出門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.80,0:20:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我太太最近常常和朋友到外面喝酒喝到很晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.60,0:20:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想大概中午才會起床吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.30,0:20:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣 就不用懷疑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.30,0:20:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我的推理是正確的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.80,0:20:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯人躲藏的地方應該是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.70,0:20:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個有遮簾的書櫃裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.60,0:20:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.30,0:20:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這真的是太好了 裡面的書也不多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.40,0:20:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很容易躲人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.30,0:20:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且裡面的東西也很少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.90,0:20:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有這個簾子與其他簾子不同 是橘紅色的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.70,0:20:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個簾子是為了改變房間色調所以剛掛上去不久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.50,0:20:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他的簾子也準備換了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.90,0:20:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是這種地方能夠躲人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.80,0:20:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要拿掉兩塊隔板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.10,0:20:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個大人都可以很輕鬆地躲進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.30,0:21:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說 犯人的做法就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.40,0:21:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯人曾調查過這裡的生活習慣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.50,0:21:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後趁主人離開的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.90,0:21:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在夫人起床之前偷偷進入這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.90,0:21:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再躲到這個書架裡面等待機會殺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.30,0:21:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等待被害者騎上電動車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.60,0:21:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,背後一點防衛也沒有的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.50,0:21:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是卻很難找到機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.30,0:21:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在這時 不知是幸還是不幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.60,0:21:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,員警那裡打了電話進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.20,0:21:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慌張的犯人從書架上跳出來然後把人殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.10,0:21:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,入侵途徑是被割了洞的窗戶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.20,0:21:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.20,0:21:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,增尾先生講過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.90,0:21:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她太太在家裡看到過附近有可疑人物徘徊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.60,0:21:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以因為這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.10,0:21:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而知道被害者的作息時間和習慣也不足為奇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.20,0:22:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對 這個推理有個很大的漏洞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.20,0:22:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯人絕對是這個傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.80,0:22:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過他是怎麼能夠從離家裡幾十公里的警視廳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.50,0:22:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用什麼方法殺害太太的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.70,0:23:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一個人可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.80,0:23:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠將它恢復原狀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.20,0:23:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,需要一些技巧的人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.30,0:24:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 你們有什麼證據證明人是我殺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.90,0:24:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 大叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.40,0:24:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的手指好像被什麼東西刺過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.80,0:24:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一集 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.20,0:24:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本廳的刑事戀愛故事（後篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.80,0:24:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.60,0:24:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,書櫃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.40,0:24:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,次回是後篇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.60,0:24:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤小姐 喜歡…滑雪嗎
